issue_comments.body:
We do not use the "assign" feature of the GH (it makes lots of sense in an organization where everyone working on the code is an employee in a reporting chain and part of the org, it makes less sense in a community project where most contributors are volunteers and many are not in the org).

I have re-milestoned this to 3.5 (the next-next feature release) because we are aiming to have 3.4 out "soon", this is not something we should block 3.4 on and work has not started yet.

@CharlesHe16 If you are interested in working on this that would be great :)
